high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the end of the large wooden table.
Pick up the furthest box of tissues off of the large wooden table.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk across the room to the wooden table that the television is on.
Put the box of tissues on the wooden table.
Walk around the wooden table to the small round table in the corner of the room in front of you.
Pick up the box of tissues off of the small round table.
Walk back over to the wooden table that the television is on.
Put the box of tissues on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Move two boxes of tissues to a wooden table.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the table
Pick up the tissue box on the table
Turn left, go forward, turn right and go to the tv stand
Put the tissue box on the tv stand
Move around the tv stand and go to the round coffee table
Pick up the tissue box on the coffee table
Turn left, go to the left of the tv stand
Put the tissue box on the tv stand
anns.task_desc: Put two tissue boxes on the tv stand

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the left side of the table where the three tissue box boxes are.
Pick up the box of tissue box that is in the back of the other two.
With the tissue box in hand go to the left side of the tv.
Place the tissue box on the tv stand to the left of the tv.
Go to the tv tray in the corner that is to the right of the tv.  Go to the side where the tissue box is.
Pick up the tissue box that is on the tv stand.
With the tissue box in hand go to the left side of the tv stand.
Place the tissue box to the left of the tissue box that is on the tv stand.
anns.task_desc: Move two tissue boxes to the tv stand.
